javax.xml.soap

Class MimeHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.xml.soap.MimeHeader

  • public class MimeHeader
extends Object
    An object that stores a MIME header name and its value. One or more MimeHeader objects may be contained in a MimeHeaders object.
